SHIELD digs deeper into the mystery of Jimmy Woo's golden age team to find out how one becomes a GORILLA MAN! What they find leads to the hidden location of the mind-clouding beauty VENUS. It's the greatest flying saucer ride of the year!.,2006,9
32 PGS./Rated T+ ...$2.99
